Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.98,0:00:13.34,Show Title,,0,0,0,,{\fs142.5\fnGallow Tree\4aFF\pos(443.949,598.286)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.99,0:00:15.26,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.69,0:00:18.78,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,with its armies\Nstraight from hell
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.32,0:00:22.88,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows\Nthreaten us all
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.88,0:00:26.59,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.59,0:00:30.32,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.32,0:00:33.34,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,With my shining machine...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.85,0:00:36.60,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.45,0:00:40.11,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.07,0:00:44.70,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.70,0:00:48.36,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.36,0:00:50.81,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.86,0:00:54.49,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.49,0:00:59.08,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.08,0:01:02.56,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.38,0:01:10.85,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Hongo Takeshi is the Kamen\NRider, a cyborg.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.85,0:01:12.94,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He was modified by the evil\NShocker, a secret
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.94,0:01:14.76,Narrator,,0,0,0,,organization plotting\Nworld domination.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.76,0:01:18.47,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider has pledged to\Nfight Shocker and free humanity!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.91,0:01:24.89,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx95\fs130\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(477.167,140.389)}The Monstrous Beaded Lizard Man
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.91,0:01:24.89,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs135\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(477.167,680.389)}Deathmatch in Fear Valley!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.36,0:01:32.03,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\an9\c&H46B6DB&\3c&H160E05&}Otaguro\N Research Institute
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.66,0:01:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yamamoto, the X-Alpha fluid.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.87,0:01:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.79,0:01:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.69,0:01:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think we can really revive a\Ndog that's been dead for three weeks?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.55,0:02:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Is everything in place?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.59,0:02:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.98,0:02:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor! The dog's alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.37,0:02:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor! Doctor Otaguro!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.93,0:02:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yamamoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.38,0:02:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.92,0:02:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yoshiko...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.64,0:02:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We've finally done it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.20,0:02:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.06,0:02:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,We brought a dog that's been dead\Nfor three weeks back to life.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.09,0:02:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.41,0:02:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.83,0:02:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.81,0:02:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yamamoto.\N- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.10,0:02:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that we know the\NX-Alpha fluid works,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.08,0:02:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,we must begin clinical trials at\NJohoku University first thing tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.45,0:02:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.62,0:02:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Take the X-Alpha fluid\Nto the university for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.52,0:02:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.70,0:02:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll see you later, Yoshiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.14,0:02:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.22,0:02:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you. I owe it all to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.71,0:02:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Really, Doctor...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.92,0:03:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.40,0:03:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.28,0:03:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,- Wh-What are you doing?\N- You must die!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.71,0:03:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the kind of man who always\Ngets whatever he wants...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.63,0:03:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.62,0:03:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Run, if you think you can...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.65,0:03:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But you cannot escape\Nthe great Beaded Lizard Man!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.69,0:04:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.57,0:04:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yoshiko...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.65,0:04:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.49,0:04:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you kill him?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.69,0:04:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,If you had left Yamamoto alive,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.55,0:04:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,we could have extracted the\Nsecret of the X-Alpha from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.69,0:04:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,We should just abduct\NDoctor Otaguro himself and...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.16,0:04:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait. Just wait a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.72,0:04:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,If we kidnap Otaguro\Nnow, Rider will catch on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.86,0:04:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Then...\Nshould we give up on the X-Alpha?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.46,0:04:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.24,0:04:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker must obtain the\NX-Alpha at any cost,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.53,0:04:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,to further advance our\Nown scientific prowess.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.12,0:04:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at the screen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.02,0:04:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,This woman is Otaguro's other\Nassistant, Yoshiko Hashimoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.75,0:05:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The only way to complete the plan to\Nenhance our scientific capabilities
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.31,0:05:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,by stealing the secret of the\NX-Alpha, without Rider catching on,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.92,0:05:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,is to use this woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.28,0:05:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.03,0:05:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Steal the secret of the X-Alpha\Nfluid without Rider catching on!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.40,0:05:25.72,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Shocker's plan was to use\Ntwo doctors from England
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.72,0:05:28.36,Narrator,,0,0,0,,who died two years ago,\Nsaid to be the greatest in their fields...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.36,0:05:32.04,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The physicist, Doctor Edward,\Nand the mathematician, Doctor Kaines...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.04,0:05:35.23,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Whose bodies they stole from\Ncold storage in a London museum,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.23,0:05:36.92,Narrator,,0,0,0,,revive them with\Nthe X-Alpha fluid,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.92,0:05:39.66,Narrator,,0,0,0,,and force them to create\Ndeadly weapons for Shocker.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.52,0:05:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, Beaded Lizard Man.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.14,0:05:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Abduct Yoshiko Hashimoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.87,0:05:54.45,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\bord5\fs60\3c&HFFFFFF&\c&H160E05&}Hashimoto
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.87,0:05:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.46,0:05:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Goro, good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.91,0:05:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Kiyoshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.73,0:05:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on just a minute.\NI'll call him now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.48,0:06:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiyoshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.34,0:06:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Better hurry,\Nor Goro will leave without you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.29,0:06:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,See you later, Mom, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.42,0:06:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, hurry up, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.53,0:06:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.24,0:06:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiyoshi. Take care, would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.80,0:06:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.64,0:06:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't forget anything, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.84,0:06:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.80,0:06:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.86,0:06:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.89,0:06:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no!\NI forgot my homework again!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.70,0:06:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.54,0:06:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Go! Go to Otaguro's laboratory!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.25,0:06:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.63,0:06:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,- Help me!\N- Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.28,0:06:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Kiyoshi's sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.93,0:06:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,My sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.81,0:06:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Shocker!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.44,0:07:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Darn you, Shocker!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.44,0:07:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Your sister\Nwas taken by Shocker?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.05,0:07:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What would Shocker\Nwant with his sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.26,0:07:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think Shocker\Nmight have already...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.74,0:07:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Hush!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.32,0:07:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Tokko! Don't you even\Nrealize how Kiyoshi must feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.48,0:07:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.02,0:07:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,If they kill my\Nsister, I'll die, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.14,0:07:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be okay, Kiyoshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.29,0:07:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We have Mr. Hongo Takeshi\Nand Mr. Taki on our side.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.07,0:07:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I just know they'll\Nsave your sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.72,0:07:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, Chairman?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.88,0:07:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.99,0:07:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Goro's exactly right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.34,0:07:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on... it's not good\Nfor a boy to cry like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.45,0:07:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,If the Kamen Rider saw you\Ncrying, he'd have to laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.82,0:07:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.33,0:07:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,How's everyone doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.28,0:08:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Not well at all, I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.73,0:08:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.80,0:08:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker kidnapped\NKiyoshi's big sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.33,0:08:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.40,0:08:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,When did this happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.36,0:08:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.46,0:08:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe Kiyoshi's sister is an\Nassistant at Otaguro Laboratory.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.18,0:08:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor Otaguro is one of Japan's\Nmost famous biochemists.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.56,0:08:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, he's in my department!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.29,0:08:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,There have been rumors that he's\Ndoing some groundbreaking research...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.05,0:08:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You think Shocker is after that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.31,0:08:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki, let's head for\NOtaguro's laboratory.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.36,0:08:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.29,0:08:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yoshiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.32,0:08:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-Who are you people?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.03,0:08:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Otaguro.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.57,0:08:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish to trade the X-Alpha\Nfluid for this woman's life.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.80,0:08:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.89,0:09:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,X-Alpha?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.70,0:09:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what\Nyou're talking about!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.27,0:09:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that your final\Nword on the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.50,0:09:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Even now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.40,0:09:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.69,0:09:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute. Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.09,0:09:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give you the documents...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.44,0:09:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.80,0:09:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.29,0:09:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor! Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.86,0:09:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.31,0:09:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn... you won't get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.02,0:09:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.72,0:09:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.81,0:10:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Transformation!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.43,0:10:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,There you are, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.53,0:10:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Drop the caltrops!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.05,0:10:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.81,0:10:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.64,0:10:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.11,0:10:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Take the girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.37,0:10:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yoshiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.36,0:10:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you, Shocker...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.61,0:11:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Fight me, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.28,0:11:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Beaded Lizard Man!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.92,0:11:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.12,0:11:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.08,0:11:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yoshiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.64,0:11:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Die, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.20,0:12:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think of my venom?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.88,0:12:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,If you'd been a normal man,\Nyou'd be melted by now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.31,0:12:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,My body's... going numb!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.80,0:12:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Your end has come at\Nlast, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.17,0:12:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider, fall to hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.56,0:12:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I'll cut the rope!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.07,0:12:45.91,Bumper Episode 53-69,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fs90\pos(280,94)\c&H05008E&}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.31,0:12:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Our plan is going perfectly!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.45,0:13:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Ambassador Hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.60,0:13:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Haven't you acquired\Nthe X-Alpha fluid yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.25,0:13:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Just leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.84,0:13:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I nearly have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.52,0:13:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Beaded Lizard Man has put an end to the\NKamen Rider, our greatest obstacle.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.25,0:13:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So, next time...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.72,0:13:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Ambassador Hell,\Nthe Rider still lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.74,0:13:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.94,0:13:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You realize that failure means\Ndeath, do you not?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.59,0:13:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But I will give you\None final chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.71,0:13:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That Kamen Rider has\Nthe devil's own luck...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.56,0:13:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have to get Hongo and Taki to\Nbring Otaguro's documents themselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.65,0:13:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.11,0:13:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be all right, Kiyoshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.12,0:14:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Just eat up, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.62,0:14:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't there anything we can do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.28,0:14:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Poor kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.33,0:14:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.90,0:14:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Takeshi! You need to rest!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.48,0:14:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Taki, Pops?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.75,0:14:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Otaguro's laboratory.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.68,0:14:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Takeshi, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.05,0:14:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You're in no condition for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.50,0:14:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Let Taki handle this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.68,0:14:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.04,0:14:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You great fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.25,0:14:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Give some thought\Nto your condition!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.37,0:14:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.69,0:14:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me go, Pops!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.96,0:15:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.13,0:15:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The tests are going swimmingly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.14,0:15:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Turn off the buzzsaw.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.46,0:15:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo Takeshi and Taki will\Nsurely come to save her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.65,0:15:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,This electrical current is\Npassing through this circuit
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.38,0:15:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,and through the woman's body.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.33,0:15:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,When Hongo sees her,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.07,0:15:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,he'll try to save her by\Nturning off the electric saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.18,0:15:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,When he touches the woman,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.15,0:15:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,it will immediately\Nsend electricity through
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.67,0:15:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,the bombs placed\Nall around the base,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.80,0:15:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,causing a massive explosion!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.01,0:15:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,They're going to kill Yoshiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.33,0:15:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What... what should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.21,0:15:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, you should wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.83,0:16:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll want to ransom Yoshiko\Nto get the X-Alpha documents.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.29,0:16:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't lose our patience.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.76,0:16:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to wait for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.03,0:16:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,But there's no way we can just\Nhand them the documents...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.58,0:16:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.16,0:16:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.56,0:16:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.69,0:16:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Taki?\NInteresting show, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.36,0:16:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You're... Ambassador Hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.52,0:16:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.57,0:16:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's currently 2:15.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.72,0:16:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,At 2:30, this saw will\Nbury itself in her body.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.69,0:16:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't want her to die,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.22,0:16:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,you must bring the documentation on the\NX-Alpha fluid to Fear Valley by 2:30.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.65,0:16:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Fear Valley?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.61,0:16:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Just fifteen minutes left...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.35,0:16:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But the documents must be\Nbrought by Hongo and Taki.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.57,0:16:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.49,0:17:02.65,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\an9\c&H160E05&\3c&H385B6C&}X-Alpha-related Documents
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.66,0:17:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Take them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.86,0:17:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.25,0:17:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, save Yoshiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.30,0:17:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no replacement\Nfor a person's life.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.60,0:17:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.51,0:17:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.15,0:17:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, save Yoshiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.66,0:17:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki took the documents to\NShocker, by himself?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.88,0:17:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Transformation!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.40,0:18:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Shocker!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.17,0:18:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I brought the documents!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.98,0:18:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Come out now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.35,0:18:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki... you fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.97,0:18:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yoshiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.66,0:18:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.64,0:18:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Beaded Lizard Man,\Nthe Kamen Rider has appeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.42,0:18:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,There you are, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.42,0:18:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to watch the\Nexplosion, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.48,0:19:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Two minutes remain!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.77,0:19:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider, hurry! Hit the switch!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.73,0:19:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.60,0:19:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The switch is designed to set\Noff bombs all around the base!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.42,0:19:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,All right...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.43,0:19:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki, hurry!\NFind the explosives!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.50,0:19:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have much time! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.59,0:19:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yoshiko...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.53,0:19:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider! Hurry, before Yoshiko...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.62,0:19:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.33,0:19:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The bombs are gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.28,0:19:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm turning it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.33,0:20:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.90,0:20:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.98,0:20:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,There you are, Shocker!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.74,0:20:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki! Take Yoshiko and run!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.73,0:20:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.83,0:20:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.30,0:21:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Die, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.62,0:21:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.12,0:21:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Without that tongue,\Nhe'd be an ordinary opponent...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.40,0:21:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.43,0:21:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.28,0:21:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Head Crusher!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.49,0:22:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I have won.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.82,0:22:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiyoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.72,0:22:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.80,0:22:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Sis...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.60,0:22:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiyoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.70,0:22:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm happy for you, Kiyoshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.67,0:22:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Takeshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.81,0:22:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,- Sorry I'm late!\N- Takeshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.04,0:22:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Where have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.33,0:22:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,- Here it is.\N- Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.00,0:22:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I owe you all a great debt.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.18,0:22:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Thank you all so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.41,0:22:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, save your thanks\Nfor the doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.92,0:22:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,His willingness to\Nhand over the documents
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.85,0:22:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,is what saved your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.81,0:22:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.61,0:22:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.98,0:22:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.88,0:22:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.12,0:22:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute! Hey, hang on!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.03,0:22:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw, man...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.17,0:22:59.63,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The Kamen Rider, Hongo Takeshi,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.63,0:23:03.99,Narrator,,0,0,0,,had defeated Beaded Lizard Man and kept\Nthe X-Alpha fluid out of Shocker's hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.99,0:23:06.42,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Ride on, our Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.07,0:23:10.68,Cont,,0,60,160,,{\blur.8\fad(0,400)}To be continued
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.03,0:23:13.87,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\4aFF\bord0\b1\fs67.5\fnCalibri\pos(499.031,496.481)}Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.88,0:23:14.71,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The next assassin sent by Shocker\NHQ to kill our Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.71,0:23:16.31,Narrator,,0,0,0,,is the Monstrous Worm-Man.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.31,0:23:19.66,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He uses a terrifying killer\Nrings to throw Rider to his doom.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.66,0:23:23.04,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But Hongo Takeshi\Nrevives with Rider Power.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.04,0:23:25.58,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Go, our Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.58,0:23:30.95,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Join us next week for "The Monstrous\NWorm Man of the Bottomless Swamp!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.48,0:23:30.95,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscy90\fs105\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\1c&HF3F4F4&\b1\pos(487.167,720.389)}The Monstrous Worm Man of the Bottomless Swamp!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.89,0:23:40.73,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,He came here on a storm...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.31,0:23:43.31,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is he? Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.31,0:23:45.27,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is this man of storms,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.27,0:23:48.32,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,who sends the\Nvillains scattering?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.82,0:23:50.69,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.69,0:23:52.57,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,His mask stands for justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.57,0:23:54.36,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Start it up! Rev it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.36,0:23:55.70,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Get that engine running!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.04,0:23:58.20,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Give me top speed, Cyclone!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.25,0:24:03.90,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Hit them with\Nall of your anger!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.90,0:24:07.50,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Put an end to Shocker's evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.50,0:24:11.10,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider! Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.50,0:24:15.41,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Comment: 0,0:01:19.91,0:01:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The Monstrous Beaded Lizard Man.\NDeathmatch in Fear Valley!!